|archive-date=2017-09-04 
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904114749/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/4890642.stm 
|dead-url=no 
}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_2373717,00.html |title=Baros gives Birmingham the blues |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-04-16 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310084224/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_2373717,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。球季結束後，卡希爾終於同意續約三年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_2378486,00.html |title=Ridgewell pens new deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-05-30 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2007-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071227014904/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_2378486,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。 

[[馬田·奧尼爾|馬田·奧尼爾]]於[[2006年至2007年英格蘭超級聯賽|2006/07年球季]]接手任教維拉，而卡希爾卻因季前膝傷一直高掛免戰牌，直到2006年10月18日才為預備隊作客[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]踢足全場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_2392820,00.html |title=O'Neill has faith in Sutton |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-10-18 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2007-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071227014909/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_2392820,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。上季整季因傷缺陣後重獲正選的[[马丁·劳尔森|马丁·劳尔森]]再次觸傷[[膝蓋|膝蓋]]舊患，需休戰3個月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/6131736.stm |title=Laursen to miss next three months |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-11-10 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2015-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150529074046/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/6131736.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，卡希爾才取得上陣機會，整季上陣20場英超及1場[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]賽事。

[[2007年至2008年英格蘭超級聯賽|2007/08年球季]]維拉從[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]購入[[扎特·奈特|扎特·奈特]]後，卡希爾上陣機會進一步減少，有多支[[英冠|英冠]]球隊希望借用卡希爾<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2737876,00.html |title=Villa consider Cahill offers |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-09-18 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2007-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071227014220/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2737876,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，他在本季僅為維拉上陣兩場，於2007年9月19日被外借到兒時擁戴的[[谢周三足球俱乐部|錫周三]]的死敵[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]3個月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Blades complete Cahill loan deal |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7002782.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-09-16 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2019-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210202022/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/7002782.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。卡希爾在9月22日首次扳甲作客2-3負於[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Crystal Palace 3-2 Sheff Utd |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6996435.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-09-22 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2017-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906001902/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6996435.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；11月10日他在作客1-0擊敗[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]射入致勝球兼加盟後首個入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Stoke 0-1 Sheff Utd |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7076450.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-11-10 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2017-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906001825/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7076450.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；11月27日再下一城，協助球隊3-0大勝[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查爾頓]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7110822.stm |title=Charlton 0-3 Sheff Utd |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-11-27 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2007-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071129225400/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7110822.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。由於表現出色，有傳錫菲聯領隊[[布莱恩·罗布森|布莱恩·罗布森]]有意於轉會窗重開時將他收歸旗下<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2890123,00.html |title=Cahill rejects Blades talk |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-11-27 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2008-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080226064432/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2890123,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，最終於12月15日對[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|班士利]]後完成借用，期間合共上陣16場及射入兩球，而卡希爾表示仍未收到維拉的續約條件<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_2967509,00.html |title=Cahill waiting on Villa contact |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-12-13 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2008-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080417052041/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_2967509,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2008年1月轉會窗期間有關卡希爾前途的傳言滿天飛，傳聞維拉的對頭[[伯明翰城足球俱乐部|伯明翰城]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Birmingham thwarted in double bid |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7181949.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-14 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2009-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090202132000/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7181949.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>、[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_3077650,00.html |title=Villa snub Bolton's Cahill bid |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-01-25 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2008-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080429234809/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_3077650,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>以至[[土耳其|土耳其]]球會[[贝西克塔斯体操俱乐部|比錫達斯]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Besiktas move for Majstorovic |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_3039665,00.html |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-01-11 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2009-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090322200456/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_3039665,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，均表示有意羅致他。

====保頓====
2008年1月30日卡希爾正式加盟[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]，動筆簽約三年半，轉會費金額沒有透露<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_3095342,00.html |title=Bolton capture Cahill |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-01-30 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2008-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080409203111/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_3095342,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，其後馬田·奧尼爾透露為500萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5678793,00.html |title=O'Neill - No Cahill regrets |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-11-06 |accessdate=2010-02-10}}</ref></small>，隨即於2月2日首度上陣作客2-0擊敗[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Reading 0-2 Bolton |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7210608.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-02-02 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2017-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904114341/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7210608.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。其時保頓亦已晉級[[2007/08赛季欧洲联盟杯#淘汰賽階段|歐洲足協盃淘汰賽階段]]，2月14日卡希爾首嚐歐洲賽滋味，於32強主場迎戰[[西甲|西甲]][[马德里竞技|馬德里體育會]]，協助球隊1-0獲勝<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/7236400.stm |title=Bolton 1-0 Atletico Madrid |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-02-14 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2008-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080217213825/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/7236400.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，再於次回合0-0守和對手，累計1-0晉級；16強對[[里斯本竞技|士砵亭]]才累計僅負1-2被淘汰<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/7285151.stm |title=S Lisbon 1-0 Bolton (agg 2-1) |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-03-13 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2008-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080406233042/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/7285151.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。保頓護級形勢一度吃緊，幸而最後一場前的4場-{比}-賽取得3勝1和佳績<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_3528956,00.html |title=Cahill hails Bolton bottle |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-05-06 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310080308/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_3528956,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，5月11日聯賽煞科賽1-1賽和仍有些微希望奪標的[[切尔西足球俱乐部|車路士]]，成功護級<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7381780.stm |title=Chelsea 1-1 Bolton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-05-11 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2020-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200527020820/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7381780.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。而季尾時卡希爾亦獲選為「保頓最佳新加盟球員」（''Best Newcomer''）。

[[2008年至2009年英格蘭超級聯賽|2008/09年球季]]卡希爾獲領隊[[加里·麥格森|加里·麥格森]]（Gary Megson）分發以前由[[阿卜杜拉耶·梅特|美迪]]（Abdoulaye Méïté）穿著的「5」號球衣。2008年8月26日[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]對[[北安普顿足球俱乐部|諾咸頓]]，他於38分鐘因侵犯對手被罰[[紅牌|紅牌]]離隊，大部分時間10人應戰的保頓亦爆冷1-2不敵提早出局<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/7576347.stm |title=Bolton 1-2 Northampton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-26 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2008-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080921063511/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/7576347.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。10月5日作客[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]，卡希爾射入加盟以來首個入球，協助球隊3-1取得勝仗<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7639504.stm |title=West Ham 1-3 Bolton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-10-15 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2010-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101004193349/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7639504.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2009年8月10日卡希爾續約保頓三年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5482772,00.html |title=Cahill signs new Bolton deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-08-10 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2009-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090917155108/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5482772,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。[[2009年至2010年英格蘭超級聯賽|2009/10年球季]]球隊開季成績差劣，3場主場賽事僅得1分，於1-1賽和[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]後遭主場球迷喝倒采，卡希爾呼籲球迷支持球隊<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5573979,00.html |title=Cahill appeals to Bolton fans |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-09-21 |accessdate=2010-02-09}}</ref></small>，但領隊加里·麥格森最終在12月30日被辭退<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/8434719.stm |title=Bolton Wanderers sack manager Gary Megson |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-12-30 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2009-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091231025953/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/8434719.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，卡希爾表示永遠感謝加里·麥格森將他改造成一個更佳的球員<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5830693,00.html |title=Cahill thankful to Megson |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-01-04 |accessdate=2010-02-10}}</ref></small>。本季他演出神勇，以後防球員身份攻入7球，直到2010年2月初仍是球隊的首席射手。保頓新任領隊[[欧文·科尔|欧文·科尔]]（Owen Coyle）透露他在獲得確實卡希爾不會離隊才決定接手<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5917556,00.html |title=Coyle - Cahill stay crucial |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-02-04 |accessdate=2010-02-10 |archive-date=2010-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100208233943/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5917556,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

卡希爾在操練時左臂疼痛及腫脹，被迫退出在2010年2月6日主場對[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]的賽事，並在醫院渡過週末，檢查發現手臂內有血凝塊，預計需要休戰數個月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Gary Cahill injury blow for Bolton Wanderers |url=http://www.theboltonnews.co.uk/sport/4994228.Gary_Cahill_injury_blow_for_Bolton_Wanderers/ |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-02-08 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2017-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904111217/http://www.theboltonnews.co.uk/sport/4994228.Gary_Cahill_injury_blow_for_Bolton_Wanderers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。3月20日卡希爾在作客對[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]復出擔任沒有上陣的後備，兩天後為預備隊對[[曼城足球俱乐部|曼城]]踢足全場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/8580762.stm |title=England prospect Gary Cahill makes reserves comeback |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-03-22 |accessdate=2010-03-23 |archive-date=2010-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100323054453/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/8580762.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

===車路士===
英超車路士在冬季轉會窗，成功由保頓羅致二十六歲的英格蘭後衛加利卡希爾，傳媒報道，轉會費約七百萬鎊，加利卡希爾說，車路士是一間爭標的大球會，對他而言是重大機遇，難以拒絕加盟。加里卡希爾，將會取代巴西後衛[[阿歷斯|阿歷斯]]的位置，而阿歷斯由於喪失正選地位，經領隊[[保亞斯|保亞斯]]的一輪雪藏後於一月轉會窗加盟[[巴黎聖日耳門|巴黎聖日耳門]]。

2012年5月19日，加里卡希爾以先發的身分參了切爾西與拜仁慕尼黑的歐冠決賽。並隨隊奪得了歐冠冠軍。同年他的舊東家博爾頓慘遭降級，這使得他在冬歇期加盟切爾西的轉會，成為了史上最明智的轉會。

