==國家隊生涯==
卡希爾曾代表[[英格蘭19歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U19]]參賽，2005年代表[[英格蘭20歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U20]][[友誼賽|友賽]]俄羅斯及荷蘭<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/MensUnder20s/NewsAndFeatures/2009/Eng21_vHolland_TeamNamed.aspx |title=U20s pass Russian test |publisher=[[英格蘭足球總會|''thefa.com'']] |date=2005-02-08 |accessdate=2010-02-10 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411214228/https://www.thefa.com/England/MensUnder20s/NewsAndFeatures/2009/Eng21_vHolland_TeamNamed.aspx }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/MensUnder20s/NewsAndFeatures/2009/EngU20_vHolland_Oct05.aspx |title=Lions checked by Dutch |publisher=[[英格蘭足球總會|''thefa.com'']] |date=2005-10-09 |accessdate=2010-02-10 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411205834/https://www.thefa.com/England/MensUnder20s/NewsAndFeatures/2009/EngU20_vHolland_Oct05.aspx }}</ref></small>，但由於祖父母的關係亦有權代表[[愛爾蘭國家足球隊|愛爾蘭]]，時任愛爾蘭領隊[[史蒂夫·史當頓|史蒂夫·史當頓]]曾與他傾談相關事宜<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_2373989,00.html |title=Cahill could join Eire |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-04-19 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310084229/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_2373989,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2007年2月1日剛上任[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]主帥的[[斯图尔特·皮尔斯|皮雅斯]]徵召卡希爾入伍，他與[[马修·德比夏尔|達比舒亞]]及[[乔·哈特|乔·哈特]]是隊中三張新面孔<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11676_2404273,00.html |title=Three new faces for U21s |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-02-01 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2008-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080223194546/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11676_2404273,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，惟沒有獲派在2月6日對[[西班牙21歲以下國家足球隊|西班牙]]的賽事上陣<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6322149.stm |title=England U21 2-2 Spain U21 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-02-06 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2007-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070214062042/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6322149.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。他首次代表英格蘭U21是於3月24日新[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]揭幕賽迎戰[[義大利21歲以下國家足球隊|義大利]]，與[[安东·费迪南德|安东·费迪南德]]合作防守中路，最終3-3平手完場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6483789.stm |title=England U21s draw Wembley cracker |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-03-24 |accessdate=2010-02-09 |archive-date=2007-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070823030430/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6483789.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；接著於6月5日[[友誼賽|友賽]][[斯洛伐克21歲以下國家足球隊|斯洛伐克]]繼續正選上陣，但拍檔則換上[[斯蒂芬·泰勒|斯蒂芬·泰勒]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/MensUnder-21Team/NewsAndFeatures/2007/EngU21s_vSlovakiaReport.aspx |title=Five star send off |publisher=[[英格蘭足球總會|''thefa.com'']] |date=2007-06-05 |accessdate=2010-02-10 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411203944/https://www.thefa.com/England/MensUnder-21Team/NewsAndFeatures/2007/EngU21s_vSlovakiaReport.aspx }}</ref></small>。卡希爾入選英格蘭U21參賽在[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]舉行的[[2007年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2007年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]決賽週大軍名單<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6702087.stm |title=Bentley picked for England U21s |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-30 |accessdate=2010-02-10 |archive-date=2007-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070920173114/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6702087.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。揭開賽由於安东·费迪南德及斯蒂芬·泰勒因傷及停賽而缺陣，由卡希爾配搭原任右閘的[[內姆·奧奴夏|內姆·奧奴夏]]鎮守中路<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.uefa.com/under21/news/newsid=550357.html#cahill+expects+testing+night |title=Cahill expects testing night |publisher=[[UEFA|''uefa.com'']] Sport |date=2007-06-14 |accessdate=2010-02-10 |archive-date=2017-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171028223457/http://www.uefa.com/under21/news/newsid=550357.html#cahill+expects+testing+night |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，成功抵擋[[捷克21歲以下國家足球隊|捷克]]的攻擊，保持清白0-0完場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6738781.stm |title=Czech Rep U21 0-0 England U21 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-06-11 |accessdate=2010-02-10 |archive-date=2007-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070909122225/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6738781.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，是他在賽事中唯一上陣的一場，亦是最後一場代表U21上陣。

2009年6月2日卡希爾獲[[英格蘭足球代表隊|國家隊]]徵召備戰對[[哈萨克斯坦国家足球队|哈薩克斯坦]]的[[2010年世界盃外圍賽_(歐洲區)|2010年世界盃外圍賽]]，代替因傷退隊的[[里奧·費迪南|里奧·費迪南]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Rio out of England squad |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12098_5359839,00.html |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-06-02 |accessdate=2010-02-10 |archive-date=2009-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090724045540/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12098_5359839,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；9月2日又被召入伍作為有輕傷在身的[[約翰·泰利|約翰·泰利]]和[[韦斯·布朗|韦斯·布朗]]的替補<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5532226,00.html |title=Cahill receives Capello call |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-09-02 |accessdate=2010-02-10 |archive-date=2010-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100105205227/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5532226,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；10月6日再被召代替[[乔莱昂·莱斯科特|乔莱昂·莱斯科特]]備戰[[烏克蘭國家足球隊|烏克蘭]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5614131,00.html |title=England make two changes |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-10-06 |accessdate=2010-02-10 |archive-date=2010-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100204083524/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5614131,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，惟均未能進入18人的出場名單內。

